00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:07,060
In his last life, the monk was Jinchanzi, the second disciple to Buddha in the West.

2
00:00:07,900 --> 00:00:14,620
Yet his arrogance led him to disregard the Dharma teachings, and as a result, the Buddha

